						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">rainwarrior wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">nmi:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;inc nmi_counter<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;rti<br /><br />wait_for_nmi:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;lda nmi_counter<br />@loop:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;cmp nmi_counter<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;bne @loop<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;rts</div></div><br />Shouldn't that be <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">beq @loop</tt>? You want to keep waiting while the frame count stays the same.</div>

